title: Sri Lanka Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Sri Lanka increased to 177 in September from 104 in August of 2022. Car Registrations in Sri Lanka averaged 2284.55  from 1997 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 15017  in September of 2015 and a record low of 83  in June of 2022. This page provides - Sri Lanka Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Sri Lanka
